&amp;lt;figure class=&amp;quot;wp-block-embed-flickr wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-flickr&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;wp-block-embed__wrapper&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
